\frac{i }{{\sqrt{5}}} &
   \frac{3 - 5\,i }{{\sqrt{55}}} &
   -\frac{2}{\sqrt{22}}
\end{bmatrix}

from  is a unitary matrix.  By , its columns

\set{
\colvector{
